thread.title: Todd

author: Todd
title: Todd
text: Ordered two "128" keys for an older cabinet. If you've ordered HON keys before, you know there are many number and letter options. My original key just had "128". So when the keys arrived with "128E" on them, I assumed they were wrong. However, they worked perfectly - don't know what the "E" was for, but luckily these folks know what they're doing. Very promptly mailed. Thanks, EasyKeys.
